  lines:
  - speakerName: Boss
    portrait: {fileID: 1984190853, guid: 1be9303cf68adf8469a107b28073a96a, type: 3}
    text: RAM is fixed. But remember, we also replaced the GPU earlier.
    showOnRightSide: 0
  - speakerName: Boss
    portrait: {fileID: 1984190853, guid: 1be9303cf68adf8469a107b28073a96a, type: 3}
    text: Let's verify that the old GPU was actually bad too.
    showOnRightSide: 0
  - speakerName: Boss
    portrait: {fileID: 1984190853, guid: 1be9303cf68adf8469a107b28073a96a, type: 3}
    text: Remove the new GPU and put the old one back in.
    showOnRightSide: 0
